Text.string: Hope you're having a good day.
Nice night for a fight, huh?
You locked and loaded, Vault Hunter? Nice.
I got to drive a cyclone the other day. Those things are the tits.
Whoa, haha. Watch where you point that thing!
Never thought of myself as much of a fighter before, but look at me now!
When the fighting first started, I thought I was screwed. But it turns out I'm pretty good at this!
Yeah, I've got a couple dozen confirmed kills. No big deal.
That's some sweet gear you've got there, Vault Hunter.
Lorelei said I could help on her next big mission. Can't wait!
The war was bad enough before the Children of the Vault came. Not many things scarier in the universe than the alliance of a corporation and a cult.
The city will bounce back. It always does. Maybe.
So you kinda just cut a path of destruction everywhere you go, huh? That's pretty sweet.
I've got a thing for this Atlas soldier. I wonder what he looks like under that helmet.
Don't worry about us. Prometheans are tough as nails.
What I lack in training, I make up for in raw badassery. Did that sound conceited? Whatever.
Sanctuary is much cooler than the corporate ships I've seen docked at the Halcyon Spaceport.
I'm ready to fight, whenever we set this ship down.
Don't worry, I'll keep an eye on Sanctuary while you're away.
I'm glad this ship's got a decent firing range. Helps keep me sharp.
Working out in space feels weird. The gravity's just a little bit off.
Gotta hit the firing range—been a while.
Sometimes I think about ending it... but then I think about Rhys' mustache and I know I have to be strong.
Atlas better get their shit together and win the war already.
Gotta get my cyclone fixed up.
We've rebuilt Promethea before. We can do it again.
Glad the Crimson Raiders decided to help us out.
I don't wanna die for Atlas, but I'll sure as hell die to keep Promethea safe.
Thinking of joining up with the Crimson Raiders if they'll have me.
Gotta get outta here and stretch my legs one of these days.
Maliwan, bandits, whatever, I'm ready for it.
Feeling real cooped up in here.
I gotta get back to the fight sooner or later.
I'm itching to kill some more Maliwan.
You know what I really miss? Donuts. Haven't had a good donut since the war started.
[burp] Shouldn't have had that last night.
Good to be on a team!
